# preprocess.py
# README
#
# Program function:
#
# Takes input string and removes specific stop words, digits and punctuation and
# outputs lower case string depending on the specific mode entered
#
# Running Instructions:
#
# Call program from terminal as python3 preprocess.py <mode> where mode can be keep-digits,
# keep-stops, and keep-symbols.
# Leaving mode empty would remove all digits, symbols and stop words.
#